high_descs: Go past the kitchen island ahead of you and turn left, then left again so that you facing the kitchen island.
Pick up the knife on the island between the vase and the fork.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink into slices.
Turn around and go back to the kitchen island.
Place the knife on the kitchen island, to the left of the spatula.
Turn back around towards the kitchen sink.
Pick up one of the tomato slices from the sink.
Turn to your right and go to the microwave, above the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the tomato slice from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room to the refrigerator on your right.
Place the tomato slice on the on the top shelf, in front of the lettuce, in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato slice in the refrigerator.

high_descs: go left around the center green table and face it
pick up the knife on the green table
turn around and face the sink behind the green table
slice the tomato in the sink
turn around and face the green table again
place the knife on the green table to the left of the spatula
return to the kitchen sink
pick up a slice of tomato in the sink
turn right, then go straight to face the stove top, then look up at the microwave
place the tomato in the microwave for several seconds, then take it out
take the tomato slice to the refrigerator
place the tomato in the center of the top shelf, then close the refrigerator door
anns.task_desc: slice a tomato, heat it up in the microwave, and store it in the refrigerator

high_descs: Go across the room toward the stove, turn left and then turn toward the table.
Pick up the knife the knife behind the vase on the table.
Turn around and head to the sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink.
Turn around back to the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Turn around and go back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn right and to the stove.
Put the slice of tomato in the microwave above the stove, cook it and take it back out.
Turn around, go across the room and head to the fridge.
Put the slice of tomato in front of the lettuce in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in the fridge.
